This paper discusses the design of Simple Knowledge Organization System (SKOS), which is a data model and vocabulary for expressing Knowledge Organization Systems (KOSs) such as thesauri and classification schemes in Semantic Web applications. This topic is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), deep learning (cs.DL), machine learning (cs.LG), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
